         <div type="translation">
            <ab>OIM 19448 recto: (1) To Sher-sher, the ... [ (2) Do not obstruct Pa-ti-Khonsu (3) son of Her-tayef-nakht with regard to (any) thing in the world. (4) Do not obstruct Pa-na son of (5) Qerdja  or any man of his. (6) Has written Amenhotep in year 11 (7) Hathyr, day 14.</ab>
